  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FEATURES & CONTENT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short interactable movies in virtual reality</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level, a different universe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The audience in your living room will watch you play in both first and third person camera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From calm to insane, from dinosaurs to aliens!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cinematic shots and subtitles included</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>GAMECINE uses both seated and standing modes in VR.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/f044bd37a3d5ab62adb6a6a513dd389f.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/9623c468ad9328dc8b5aa6b39a7c7ceb.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/b8aa50fdd119dc38542499089df9597f.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/4f3a65fd92cf7b07a05787b28f3cf241.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/8258868de7057079fe54a46da0b18139.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FEATURES & CONTENT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short interactable movies in virtual reality</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level, a different universe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The audience in your living room will watch you play in both first and third person camera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From calm to insane, from dinosaurs to aliens!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cinematic shots and subtitles included</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>GAMECINE uses both seated and standing modes in VR.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/f044bd37a3d5ab62adb6a6a513dd389f.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/9623c468ad9328dc8b5aa6b39a7c7ceb.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/b8aa50fdd119dc38542499089df9597f.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/4f3a65fd92cf7b07a05787b28f3cf241.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298620/extras/8258868de7057079fe54a46da0b18139.avif?t=1772818386\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p>",
